Package io.spine.system.server Description

Provides implementation of the System Bounded Context.
API Note:
The package is annotated @BoundedContext("_System") to provide entities of this package with one shared Model.

BoundedContexts serving entities of this package will be created with synthetic names created after names of parent BoundedContexts.
